ground)、索尼克CD(Sonic CD也称为sonic OVA)、索尼克X(SonicX)，五作中只有CD与X是日本作品。\r\n\r\n故事有继承AOSTH的内容为蓝本延续，因此也有许多人会拿AOSTH来和此影集互相比较。因为不管在世界何地或何时播放，一定会固定在每个星期六的早上播放一集，因此也被美国人称为“Saterday AM”简称“SatAM”或“Sonic the hedgehog:SatAM”，然而，由于影片的英文和游戏的英文一模一样，为了区分游戏和影片，大家都习惯称之SatAM，游戏为sonic the hedgehog。","name":"Sonic the Hedgehog","name_cn":"索尼克","tags":[{"name":"童年","count":17,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美","count":16,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1993","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动物","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"没看全","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Jaleel_White","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"刺猬索尼克","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"游戏改","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"DIC_Entertainment","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Emory_Myrick","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"冒险","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Noisy_Neighbors","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"派拉蒙","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"90年代","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Dick_Sebast","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"草尾毅","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"童年系","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美漫","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"游戏衍生","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Action","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"游戏","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"游戏改编","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"John_Grusd","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"索尼克"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"刺猬索尼克"},{"v":"音速小子索尼克"},{"v":"索尼克外传"},{"v":"Sonic the Hedgehog: The Animated Series"},{"v":"SatAM"},{"v":"ソニック・ザ・ヘッジホッグ"}]},{"key":"话数","value":"26"},{"key":"放送开始","value":"1993年9月18日"},{"key":"播放电视台","value":"ABC / The Childrens Channel / Pop (UK TV channel) / KidsCo"},{"key":"播放结束","value":"1994年12月10日"},{"key":"Copyright","value":"DIC Entertainment / Sega Corporation"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":39,"count":{"1":0,"2":1,"3":0,"4":0,"5":4,"6":16,"7":15,"8":2,"9":0,"10":1},"score":6.4},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":5,"dropp